description: Massive storage, quick transfer speed. SanDisk's SDHC memory card is perfect for the latest high-megapixel SDHC format supported cameras and HD camcorders. A Class 6 rating ensures smooth capture and playback of HD video while delivering great "don't miss a shot" performance for taking photos. When it's time to transfer hours of HD video or multiple large images to your computer, you'll appreciate its quick transfer speed. Record and capture the whole story with SanDisk Ultra SDHC, the new standard for highest-capacity flash memory cards.
title: SanDisk Ultra 4GB SDHC Class 6 Flash Memory Card Speed Up To 30MB/s, Frustration-Free Packaging- SDSDH-004G-AFFP
